# Calendar: Parked, Waitlist, Day View & Week View

Use this rule when changing AllDaySection, week/day views, or event data.

## Parked appointments

- **Color:** Orange (use `colors.event.orange` in AllDaySection).
- **Location:** Shown in AllDaySection top bar as “Parked” pills; in **day view only**, can be long-pressed and dragged onto the calendar to unpark.
- **Data:** `CalendarEvent.isParked === true`; when unparked, set `allDay: false` and set `start`/`end` to the dropped slot.
- **Drag:** Uses `calendarLayout` (top, scrollY) and `DAY_START_HOUR` (6) for y-axis; `SLOT_HEIGHT = 56` must match CalendarMiddleSection. Drop time = `DAY_START_HOUR + slotIndex` with 5‑min snap.

## Waitlist

- **Color:** Green (e.g. `#9DE684` / `colors.event.green`) for pills and indicators.
- **Data:** `CalendarEvent.waitlistAddedAt?: number | Date` (timestamp when added). Used for sort order and display.
- **Sort:** Waiting list is shown in **chronological order** (oldest first): sort by `waitlistAddedAt` ascending.
- **Display:** One person = show name; multiple = show count (e.g. “Waiting (5)”). Each entry shows **date and time** in format: `M/d  HH:mm` (e.g. `3/7  12:31`). Use `format(ts, 'M/d  HH:mm')` in pills and expanded list.
- **Week view:** Green waitlist indicator dot in day header; tap shows modal “Choose a day to drop an appointment by clicking on it.” No drag-and-drop in week view.

## Day view only: move & unpark

- **Move, unpark, resize, park:** All of these work **only in day view**. In week (and month) view they are disabled.
- **Day view:** Pass `onParkAppointment`, `onMoveAppointment`, `onResizeAppointment`, `onDragOverParkZone`, `parkZone`, `calendarLayout`, `onUnparkToSlot` so drag-and-drop and unpark from AllDaySection work.
- **Week view:** Pass `onUnparkToSlot={undefined}`, `calendarLayout={null}`, `parkZone={null}` to AllDaySection so pills and expanded list items are non-draggable; show hint “Switch to Day view to move or place appointments”.
- **Layout:** Single day; time axis (y-axis) on the left inside CalendarMiddleSection; vertical scroll for time slots.
- **Slots:** `DAY_START_HOUR = 6`, `DAY_END_HOUR = 23`, `SLOT_HEIGHT = 56` in CalendarMiddleSection; same constants used in AllDaySection for drop position.

## Week view

- **Move/unpark:** Disabled. AllDaySection gets `onUnparkToSlot={undefined}`, `calendarLayout={null}`, `parkZone={null}` so parked/waitlist pills and expanded items are static (no drag, no unpark).
- **Drag-and-drop (grid):** Disabled. Do **not** pass `onParkAppointment`, `onMoveAppointment`, `onResizeAppointment`, `onDragOverParkZone`, `getTargetDateForDrop`, or `parkZone` to CalendarMiddleSection when `variant="week-column"`.
- **Navigation:** Tapping a day (header or empty slot) must switch to **day view** and set that date: `setCurrentDate(date); setViewMode('day')`. Header tab must show “Day” active when so switched (controlled via `viewMode` prop on CalendarHeaderDynamic).
- **Layout:** One shared **time axis (y-axis)** on the left; 5 days visible at a glance; horizontal scroll for day columns; one vertical scroll for time axis + columns so they stay in sync.
- **Clipping:** Day columns and week-column content use `overflow: 'hidden'` so appointments do not bleed into adjacent columns.

## Shared constants

- `SLOT_HEIGHT = 56` (AllDaySection and CalendarMiddleSection).
- `DAY_START_HOUR = 6` for slot index → hour mapping in both AllDaySection and CalendarMiddleSection.
- Waitlist date+time format: **`M/d  HH:mm`** (e.g. `3/7  12:31`).
